{"tid":1932020,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"9:30  31台   31 看世界  : 疫症風暴","createTime":"2020-03-18T13:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T14:24:33.000Z","uid":37554,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2bc72efab4b4f4debf3bda63d8618766f9119432","tid":1932020,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:00:50.000Z","msg":"就在2019年將盡之際，湖北省突然爆發冠狀病毒疫潮，感染人數眾多之餘，更迅速向外擴散；二月，病毒在全世界散播，多個國家都有確診及死亡個案。不少國家都認為新冠狀病毒的源頭來自中國，究竟這疫潮是怎爆發的？本節目追訪武漢等中國受檢疫城市，訪問醫生、科學家、記者及當地居民，探討這世紀疫症的爆發經過及其引發的連串事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雙語廣播：<br />\n<br />\n粵語 /英文 (電視版)<br />\n<br />\n播放頻道：<br />\n<br />\n港台電視 31、31A<br />\n<br />\n播出時間：<br />\n<br />\n2020年3月18日 星期三晚上9時30分 (首播)"},{"pid":"dd807ad05a4b681e9d35eb89d6321782437ed1b5","tid":1932020,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"224010d749586752484b1b1aa5ced5166ac96221","tid":1932020,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662d451b2cbf8646e77a5e4abb1e7dbaa483b2ff","tid":1932020,"uid":28202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2ffe3f480139910c37e2c3a2289d2bac0c631b","tid":1932020,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3788f59c06ee17bba3c3806c2d3fd02cd156f4d3","tid":1932020,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:41:04.000Z","msg":"明明係美軍傳入黎，竟然冇講<i